{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act16side", "eventName": "吾導先路", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "GA-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "葬禮", "storyInfo": "指引我們的不是儀式本身，而是經歷這一切之後的我們自己。“路途只有自己能夠尋找，也只能憑自己的雙足行過。”\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g5_laterano_chapelout", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_001"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嗯，多深了？", "name": "凹眼眶的掘墓人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 10, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_006", "name2": "avg_npc_001", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 再多挖一點？", "name": "沒精神的掘墓人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_006"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 早晚都是一片廢墟，墳墓又不能裝上輪子躲天災。", "name": "沒精神的掘墓人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_006"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 人總想給自己的一輩子留下點痕跡......可惜都是癡心妄想。還不如化成灰拋進荒野哩。", "name": "沒精神的掘墓人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_006"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_006", "name2": "avg_npc_001", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那樣我們就沒活兒幹了。", "name": "凹眼眶的掘墓人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_006", "name2": "avg_npc_001", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 說得也是。", "name": "沒精神的掘墓人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_006"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_006", "name2": "avg_npc_001", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不過，我看啊，墳墓也不是給死人用的。是那些活著的人需要這些東西......這些儀式，還有一塊立在這兒的石頭。", "name": "凹眼眶的掘墓人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 人得對著這些東西告別，然後重新開始——", "name": "凹眼眶的掘墓人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_006", "name2": "avg_npc_001", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哈，直到走到自己的墳頭。", "name": "沒精神的掘墓人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_006"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g5_laterano_chapelout", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儀式的準備差不多了。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我不知道。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天......感覺不太好......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#4$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修士先生，昨天我很高興......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#4$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅塞菈姐姐和我說了好多有意思的事情......我們一起為葬禮做準備，我覺得......好像我能為媽媽做一些事了。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#4$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......應該做的事情做完了......之後呢？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#4$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我覺得......我為媽媽努力了......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#4$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是媽媽，真的能看見嗎？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#4$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我做的這些......真的有用嗎？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#4$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修士先生，您是不是經歷過很多次了......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這種時候，在......葬禮上。我......該怎麼做......才對呢？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......等葬禮結束了，我又該怎麼辦......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔。是啊，葬禮......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#7$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你年紀還小，但我不願意搪塞你。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#7$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們為了別人做的許多事，其實仍是為了我們自己。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞茜莉亞，這不是自私，而是指每個人活著所做的一切，歸根到底，只是在為“自我”塑形。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葬禮，告別，是因為有人離去，也是給自己的歇息。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為已經走過的路劃一個標記。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "許多大人......以此讓自己安寧。但是否能獲得安寧，或者是否能獲得任何東西，都不在於葬禮本身。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在於經歷這一切之後的我們自己。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回望與歇息之後，我們只能繼續前進。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前進去哪裡呢......？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這需要問你自己，塞茜莉亞。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是只有自己才能回答的問題，是你和我、每一個人，一生都要回答的問題。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......自己。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "路途只有自己能夠尋找，也只能憑自己的雙足行過。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修士先生，您呢？您知道這麼多，您的路......是怎麼樣的？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#5$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞茜莉亞，我無法回答你。我甚至不敢說自己找到了。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種探索是如此艱辛，如此的無望，簡直要讓人懷疑，道路是否真的存在......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我還沒有放棄。所以我和兄弟姐妹們稱呼自己為......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......“尋路者”。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g6_laterano_chapelin", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "ypos": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 240.0, "ypos": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "燭台，燭台在哪裡......", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......有人？是醫院那個黎博利，是叫帕蒂亞？......還有那個叫奧倫的萬國信使......）", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真的搞不懂，那男人在搞什麼名堂。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "注意你的措辭，奧倫。", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在是最好的時機。比起浪費時間辦什麼葬禮，現在要做的事情還有很多吧。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#10$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說你和這孩子的母親是熟人來著，真冷漠。", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我帶著小塞茜莉亞的消息來見安多恩時，就已經做出選擇了。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她足以讓這座城市墜下神壇。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因此，也足以動搖那位總躲在金色與紅色帷幕下的聖人......以及更多的人。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#8$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（他在說什麼......？）", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個薩科塔想毀滅他的聖城，憑藉一個混血女孩？真是骯髒。", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別把我說得像個破壞狂。我只是說，“足以”。不等於我要去做。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#8$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不如說，這件事不被付諸實踐，它作為籌碼的面額才最大。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#8$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要確保的只是小塞茜莉亞不落在教皇廳手裡......在這一點上，安多恩姑且與我同路。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#8$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫，我奉勸你一句。", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論你想拿塞茜莉亞耍什麼把戲，別忘了你曾經給先導的承諾。", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......多謝忠告，我還不介意和你們再同行一段。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恕不奉陪了。若是想消磨時間，比起葬禮，我有更好的去處。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......看來這幫人內部也不是鐵板一塊。）", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我最擔心的事情......沒想到竟然有萬國信使牽涉其中......）", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（葬禮結束，就帶塞茜莉亞離開。）", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g5_laterano_chapelout", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞茜莉亞，塞茜莉亞！", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾澤爾先生，葬禮馬上就要開始了。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安多恩，我不在乎你們的遠大理想，也沒興趣和你探討信仰問題。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但塞茜莉亞......葬禮結束後，我會和她一起離開。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去哪裡呢？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不勞您費心。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該點起蠟燭了，艾澤爾先生，去陪著塞茜莉亞吧。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g5_laterano_chapelout", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭早春的清晨，空氣中仍帶著寒意。"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩科塔的葬禮常常伴隨歡笑、音樂、甜點，偶爾點綴無傷大雅的爆炸事故。"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離去之人將與崇高聖靈融為一體，回歸天空。這值得每個人舉起酒杯為他祝願。"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有一種“葬禮”無法為薩科塔以外的族群所知："}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在某個瞬間，每一個薩科塔被巨大的悲痛扼住咽喉，無法動彈，無法喘息，無法移開目光。"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彷彿堤壩崩塌之後的浪潮，沖刷過每一個單薄的靈魂。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而今日的司提望區安魂教堂，既無前者的歡樂，亦無後者的磅礴。"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有一個瘦弱的女孩，努力揮動對她而言過分沉重的鐵鍬。"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為母親的墳塋覆上最後一抔土。"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞茜莉亞，去吧，是道別的時候了。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......媽媽......我該怎麼做？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當我以為......我是為了媽媽做這一切的時候，我覺得什麼都不怕，什麼都能做到。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽不在身邊的時候，我好像變厲害了一點點......是因為我長大了嗎？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是艾澤爾哥哥說......以後，我再也見不到你了。我就算長大了，變厲害了，變得了不起，媽媽也看不到了......對不對？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我做得好，媽媽也不會誇獎我......我犯了錯，媽媽也不會生氣了......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我長大，是為了什麼呢？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修士先生說......就算是為媽媽準備葬禮，就算是和媽媽道別，也是為了自己......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了自己，究竟是什麼意思？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我好害怕......媽媽......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#7$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前天，不認識的修士姐姐說，哭也好，笑也好，只要是自己的道別，離去的人就會接受......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#7$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不明白......媽媽，我應該哭，還是應該笑呢？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#7$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修士先生說，只能問自己......可是我，我也不知道呀......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#7$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......塞茜莉亞，不必著急。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還有很多時間。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 可惜，你沒有了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$2", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呀，好久不見。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$2"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安多恩，逮到你了。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......莫斯提馬，菲亞梅塔，我的戰友們，好久不見。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若是悼念已故者，你們來得稍晚了一點。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可以悼念下一位。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}